Package: shinymods
Title: A collection of shiny tools & modules
Version: 0.1.1.2
Authors@R: person('Martin', 'Frigaard', email = 'mjfrigaard@pm.me', role = c('cre', 'aut'))
Description: The shinymods package contains a collection of functions and tools
